        "subject": "LU-7021 osd: remove credits optimization from osd_declare_qid()",
        "message": "LU-7021 osd: remove credits optimization from osd_declare_qid()\n\nwe can't rely on the current state of dquota index as it can change\nby the time the transaction starts - a concurrent transaction can\nremove that item and our transaction will need to initialize it again.\n\nChange-Id: I45d3746b825ff600a17d74a5c9e1111caa08a14e\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
